import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Map, Navigation, Satellite, AlertTriangle, Clock, Zap } from 'lucide-react'; const MapViewToggle = ({ activeView, setActiveView }) => { const [sumoData] = useState({ intersections: 12, vehicles: 47, incidents: 1, avgSpeed: 35 }); const [tomtomData] = useState({ incidents: [ { id: 1, type: 'accident', location: 'Main St & 5th Ave', severity: 'high', eta: '15 min' }, { id: 2, type: 'construction', location: 'Broadway & 42nd', severity: 'medium', eta: '2 hours' }, { id: 3, type: 'congestion', location: 'Highway 101 N', severity: 'low', eta: '30 min' } ], congestionLevel: 'Medium', averageSpeed: 28 }); const tabs = [ { id: 'sumo', label: 'SUMO Simulation', subtitle: 'Synthetic Map', icon: }, { id: 'tomtom', label: 'TomTom Live Traffic', subtitle: 'Real Map Overlay', icon: } ]; const getSeverityColor = (severity) => { switch (severity) { case 'high': return 'text-danger-500 bg-danger-100'; case 'medium': return 'text-warning-500 bg-warning-100'; case 'low': return 'text-success-500 bg-success-100'; default: return 'text-primary-500 bg-primary-100'; } }; const getIncidentIcon = (type) => { switch (type) { case 'accident': return ; case 'construction': return ; case 'congestion': return ; default: return ; } }; return (
{/* Tab Navigation */}
{tabs.map((tab) => ( ))}
{/* Tab Content */}
{activeView === 'sumo' && (
{/* SUMO Simulation Map */}
